{"tid":1848670,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲真係真心膠 呢個時候仲撐武漢人","createTime":"2020-01-28T14:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T16:06:34.000Z","uid":67425,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"13ff84ff6671199ad68db04428237af060206077","tid":1848670,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"嗰個藍絲就係我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日問佢粉嶺人咁做啱唔啱<br />\n佢spin撚走我條問題 <br />\n冇話對錯 但佢覺得粉嶺人好自私<br />\n話咩武漢人病咗好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢咁大愛 又唔見可憐香港醫護 唔可憐粉嶺人？<br />\n仲話呢個時候要齊心協力先對抗到疫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢太多幻想 人哋都封晒關 得香港未封 <br />\n仲齊咩撚心 根本比人當係水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲藍絲可能覺得自己無私 睇嘢識得睇兩邊、持平<br />\n根本自己生命受威脅都仲要喺到大愛<br />\n宜家喺香港 發燒武漢人根本愈嚟愈多<br />\n香港咁撚迫 一爆發起嚟 分分鐘死得仲快過湖北"},{"pid":"061d56ea7e930d403a585d75ddd1156ff21c7a9f","tid":1848670,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:58:11.000Z","msg":"私了佢"},{"pid":"7fd0c0734a2f9d9091486e9698b5b6c65a7bbf9d","tid":1848670,"uid":36701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"叫佢上武漢撐啦，喺香港講有鬼用"},{"pid":"2e0bbdce4f62ceb8893fc73cef37bd6ff6ebc703","tid":1848670,"uid":160348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"請佢去武漢玩，去唔到武漢都去長沙"},{"pid":"4b1556595873c3727691a5bf2ae09bb2403cfc1e","tid":1848670,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"睇新聞 影住澳門好多人想過關堆哂一齊 跟住我老母講左句 嘩 咁多人堆埋一齊實死啦 <br />\n<br />\n我老豆就正義上身話：死咩啊死 睇新聞就睇新聞啦你 咁多野講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a074e0c9b683c294bc9d107cc185ea3cf21634","tid":1848670,"uid":264974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020